text:
The wanton saves the day. It was very tasty with good fried fish (tikpoh) taste. The soup was mediocre. Noodle was too soggy and the chilli was not nice. The char siew was cut very thinly and not tasty.
Service was really slow.

Noodles with black sauce are springy and QQ in texture.

Charsiew, veges and boiled dumplings are good too.

Fried wantons with mayo are delicious - must order.

Paynow or cash only.

So this is the wanton? Without any filling yet thin and small like wth.

Wanton is not freshly cooked as they were pre-cooked and left it aside.
Love the wanton noodles. Noodles is chewy.  Love the flavor mix with tomato sauce and chilli sauce. Wanton is crispy.
Really a bad experience after trying to order from them through grabfood. Not only did they not read the order notes, they also missed out my fried wanton. Really bad wont ever come back again.
